condition.narrative: No later than thirty (30) days after the Effective Date, establish and maintain, throughout Project implementation, a Working Groupled by the PIU, with the composition and functions set forth in the Project Operational Manual.

No later than thirty (30) days after the Effective Date, establish and thereafter operate and maintain, throughout Projectimplementation a Steering Committee responsible for Project oversight and coordination, led by MLSPP, and with the composition andfunctions set forth in the Project Operational Manual.

No later than two (2) months after the Effective Date, approve and implement an annual training program on the Environmental andSocial Standards, according to the terms and conditions set forth in the Project Operational Manual.
